 Syntax:  .emote [']<action>
          ;[']<action>

Results:  Allows you to perform an action or pose. Your name appears in
          front of the action you specify. If a ' is specified before
          the action, it will become posessive.

Example:  If Cygnus types -->  ;smiles    
          People in the same room will see -->  Cygnus smiles

See also: semote
